_sText:
This is a small combat surf map I made to announce that - I'm back! :)


Features:

- 15 secs protect (at the round start),

- no fall damage,

- 2 laser cannons,

- steered ufo,

- text nades,

- optimalization (about 300 fps almost all the time),


RPG mod is recommended.


Map video: 
 <iframe width="450" height="338" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/h2d5bsgx2ZY?rel=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>

Let me know if you find any bugs ;)
Have fun!
